Name: collective.portlet.bilingualtext
Version: 0.2.0
Summary: A bi-lingual text portlet for Plone 3
Home-page: http://plone.org
Author: Andreas Jung
Author-email: info@zopyx.com
License: ZPL
Description: Introduction
        ============
        
        This portlet provides to text fields for German and English text.
        It is similar to the standard Plone text portlet. The German or
        English text is displayed based on the current language.
        
